Folder containing the files for allocation (based on LPJ-GUESS; Sitch et al., 2003; Smith 2001)

module_allocation.f90 : contains the functions for carbon distribution among the compartments

program_allocation.f90 : it only calls the functions writen at module_allocation.f90

Allocation_Philip.py: original script developed by Philip

allocation_logic_description.docx: describes the logic (structured portuguese) for allocation based on the Philip's code

module_constants.f90: constants used in allocation script

module_allometry.f90 : constains the functions of allometry (these functions use the allocation)

program_allometry.f90 : it only calls the functions writen at module_allometry.f90
